@cesnaruolam Hi, Ces. You may rebook your flight thru our website by clicking the “Manage Booking” tab on our website’s homepage.

If your booking was issued by a travel agency, you may coordinate with them directly for further assistance with your ticket servicing requests.

Thank you.
